Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:14.66,Default,,0,0,0008,,{\blur3}宇宙:宇宙中的上帝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上溯至宇宙初始 周遭还只是一片漆黑{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the beginning, there was darkness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知何时 忽地一声巨响{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And then... Bang!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}时间空间以及物质皆由此发端{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Giving birth to an endless expanding existence{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}此后不断膨胀 延伸 永无止境{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of time, space, and matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每一天 新的发现都在不断为我们解开{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Every day, new discoveries are unlocking{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕴藏于这里的那些神秘莫测{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the mysterious, the mind-blowing,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}令人大开眼界 致命的秘密{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the deadly secrets of a place we call{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们称这个地方为"宇宙"{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}审视地球难以置信的复杂多样性{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Looking at the Earth's incredible complexity,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类一直想要探寻其形成的原因{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}people have always wondered what made it all possible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}物理方程式是如何发挥作用的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What breathed fire into the equations of physics.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长期以来 宗教对此有精神阐释{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Religion has long offered a spiritual explanation,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}认为上帝创造了整个宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that God created the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.53,0:00:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}目前的科学是否找到上帝存在的蛛丝马迹{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But is science now starting to find elusive evidence of God{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}物理学能否证明我们根本就不需要造物者{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}or does physics tell us that no creator was necessary?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}史蒂芬·霍金和我在《大设计》中写道{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Stephen Hawking and I say in the book, The Grand Design,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:00:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宇宙的形成可能是一个从无到有的过程{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that the universe could have come from nothing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我们开始在宇宙中进行对上帝的科学探索{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Let's embark on a scientific search for God in the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}整个宇宙其实非常狂暴{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The universe can be a very violent place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}星系之间经常碰撞{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Where galaxies routinely collide.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}耗尽的恒星不断发生爆炸{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And exhausted stars... explode.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但也是在这里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But it is also a place{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诞生了超凡脱俗之物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that gave birth to something absolutely extraordinary,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少地球上{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}at least here on Earth,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诞生了有意识情感的生命{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}conscious, sentient beings.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宇宙中为何会出现智慧生命的原因{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It is, of course, a mystery to why the universe exists{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}令人难以捉摸{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in such an intelligible manner,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但至少对我而言{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but it suggests me at least,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:01:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宇宙 其逐渐展开的宏大计划{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that there's a deep link between the universe,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以及像我们一样的生命之间有着很深的联系{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the grand scheme that's unfolding, and beings like ourselves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宇宙自知的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Somehow the universe has become self-aware.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它造出了像人类这种有思维有理解力的生命{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's engineered the emergence of comprehending, thinking beings{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有能力去探索宇宙的秘密{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}like ourselves, who can come to know the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}另许多人倍感惊奇的是{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Some people marvel at the fact that{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宇宙拥有几百亿年的历史{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the universe has over billions of years,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诞出能够领会其复杂性的生命{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}giving birth to beings who can appreciate its complexity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们现在甚至开始思索 人类从何而来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We can even ponder where and how we fit in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是在人类历史初期{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But at the dawn of history,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人们认为自己知道此类深奥问题的答案{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}people thought they knew the answers to these profound questions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古人将世界看做一个雪景球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The ancients viewed their world as a snow globe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地球是平的 像个碟子 上面盖着天穹{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's essentially a flat earth, say a disc, covered by a dome.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}英语里称作天穹{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And we call this, in English, a firmament,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恒星和行星即悬在那里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and in the firmament is where all the stars and planets were hung.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所有的古代文明相信{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Almost all ancient cultures believed{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们所在的宇宙都是在这样的一个弯顶下{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}their universe existed in a dome similar to this one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们从没质疑过谁是造物主的问题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And they never questioned who created it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古人认定是上帝或者诸神{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The ancients assumed that there was a God or gods{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}创造并维持了宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}responsible for the creation and the maintenance of the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上帝创造了宇宙这一观点{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The idea that God created the universe{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直到中世纪才遭到质疑{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}went largely unchallenged until the Middle Ages,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当时的科学家根据他们的观察{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}when scientists made a sacrilegious suggestion,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}提出了亵渎神明的想法{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}based on their observations...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宇宙的中心不是地球 而是太阳{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The Sun, not the Earth, was at the center of the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类的思维模式发生了改变{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}There was a paradigm shift.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}产生了解释我们周围自然现象的新方式{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}There is now another way to explain the natural occurring phenomena around us,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而这就是科学{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and this is science.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从中世纪开始{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Since the Middle Ages,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}科学家们发展出了许多复杂的新理论{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}scientists have developed sophisticated new theories{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以描述宇宙的宏大以及地球所处的位置{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}about the enormity of the universe and our place in it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这些理论中往往都没有上帝的立足之地{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}theories that often have no room for God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}许多现象曾对人类来说非常神秘{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Many phenomena have appeared mysterious or miraculous or magical,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而通过科学研究{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and then through the process of science,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类慢慢开始理解这些现象{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we've eventually understood them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}科学家们慢慢意识到 太阳仅仅是{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Scientists gradually realized that the Sun really is just one star{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}巨大的星系中的一颗恒星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}among a multitude of stars in a gigantic galaxy{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而这个星系拥有数以亿计颗类似恒星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}having hundreds of billions of such stars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所有这一切都始于137亿年前的一次大爆炸{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And all this was created in a Big Bang 13.7 billion years ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尽管科学理论 科学观察和实验{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But while scientific theories, observations, and experiments{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}告诉我们人类在宇宙中的位置{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}tell us where we are in the cosmos,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它们仍未回答两个永恒的问题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they don't answer the eternal questions:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即人类产生的原因{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Why we are here{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若有造物主 它又是谁{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and who, if anyone, created us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一些物理学家继续探索这些问题的答案{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So some physicists continue to search for those answers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们的发现十分惊人{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What they're finding is extraordinary.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隐藏的非凡秩序支配着整个宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}A remarkable unseen order that may govern the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类为自然世界之美所倾倒{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We're all struck by the beauty and majesty of the natural world, about us,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}树木 天空 还有日落之美{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the trees, the sky and the beauty of a sunset.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此神奇 如此壮观{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It is awesome and it's majesty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们如何才能了解这一切呢{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}How can we make sense of it all?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们需要了解自然的潜台词{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We need to look at the hidden subtext of nature,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是支持这个世界的数学关系{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the mathematical relationships that underpin it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}形成某种影子世界{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}forming a sort of shadow world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有人将其视作宇宙密码{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Some people think of this as a cosmic code.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管这些科学家是不是信仰上帝{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Regardless of whether or not they believe in God,{\r}
