Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使整个宇宙中的物质分布恰到好处{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But even with the right distribution of matter throughout the universe,{\r}
