Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我从没见过任何科学家会否认{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I don't know a single scientist who would disagree with the statement{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个世界无比精妙这个说法{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that the world is exceedingly ingenious...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不仅是数学意义上的 不仅美丽优雅{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Not just mathematical, not just beautiful, not just elegant,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是对无与伦比之事物的完美诠释{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but the manifestation of something truly extraordinary.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宇宙这种非凡的至臻之极{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}How could this extraordinary fine-tuning of the universe{\r}
