Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:09:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人们说这种至臻之极绝对证明了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's often said that the delicate fine-tuning{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}存在某种力量精心调配出这一切{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}must be evidence that some agency tuned it that way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但大多数物理学家都持不同看法{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Most physicists' take on this is actually not to go in that direction.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你再物理学中发现经过精密调整的事物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}When you see something that's finely tuned in physics,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这往往意味着{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it usually means there's a mechanism{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有尚未知晓的机制{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that you don't yet understand{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在当中发挥作用{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that is playing a role there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使看起来像是有位神圣造物主创造了宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So, while it appears a divine creator planned the universe,{\r}
