Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是除了上帝 还有什么事物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But what other than God could possibly explain{\r}
