Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最终导致宇宙中生命的诞生{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that led to the creation of life in our universe?{\r}
