Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}称之为多宇宙论{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's the multiple-universe theory.{\r}
