Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}存在数量极多的宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}perhaps even an infinite number,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个数量甚至可能是无限的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}could, in principle exist in a vast hyperspace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用一杯啤酒作比喻{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We can understand the idea of hyperspace{\r}
