Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啤酒杯中的气泡外表几乎相同{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The bubbles in a beer mug are all physically about the same.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}设想一下 它们的属性成分可能不一样{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But suppose they span a range of properties.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有一些含有碳 氧{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Some of them might have carbon, oxygen{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恒星和重力 其它的可能没有{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and stars and gravity, and others don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而我们则是其中一个宇宙 富饶 复杂{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We would be in one of the ones that leads to a rich, complex universe{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最终诞生出生命{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}combinating with life as we know it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果真有无限的宇宙 而这种精密调配{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If there are an infinite number of other universes{\r}
