Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.72,0:42:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}随着科学进步 上帝的能力逐步减弱{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The role of God has been pushed back by the advance of science.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.78,0:42:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过 这并不是科学与上帝之战{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Nevertheless, it is not a battle between the two.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.27,0:42:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类将一直处于对未知世界的探索阶段{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I don't think there'll ever be a time when we understand everything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.87,0:42:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}世界上总会存在未解之谜{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I think there'll always be the unknown.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.36,0:42:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们也会有无能为力之处{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}There'll always be a frontier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.21,0:43:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以现阶段我们总会有{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So there will always be questions that are beyond our ability to answer them{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.85,0:43:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}未解之事{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}at a current time,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.44,0:43:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但同时也有希望{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but then there's always hope{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.64,0:43:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们能在未来更好的了解这些事物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that we might explain things better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.03,0:43:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}物理学和数学永远都解释不了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Physics and mathematics can never explain{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.47,0:43:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}定律与逻辑从何而来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}where the laws or where logic came from.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.14,0:43:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为这是一切的初始{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's where we start from, and{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.73,0:43:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果有人要说 上帝创造了万物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}if people want to say, "Well, that must come from God,"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.68,0:43:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们肯定不会去辩驳他{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We certainly don't argue against that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.23,0:43:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从某些方面来说 物理定律就像{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In some ways, the laws of physics{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.51,0:43:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}神学家心中的上帝一般永恒不灭{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}are as eternal as God is to a theologian.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.76,0:43:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我们可以想象 存在于世间{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But we could imagine that there's something underpinning{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.28,0:43:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}维持并解释自然规律的因素{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the laws of nature, upholding them, explaining them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.40,0:43:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么它们是数学层面的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Why are they mathematical?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.82,0:43:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么它们自身性质会是这样{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Why do they have the properties that they do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.86,0:43:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么它们又是浅显易懂{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Why are they intelligible?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.49,0:43:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上帝不一定就是问题的答案{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'm not sure God is the right answer to this,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.50,0:43:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为上帝是文化的产物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}'cause of the cultural baggage that goes with it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.81,0:43:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我认为 就这样接受了匪夷所思之事{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but I do think that accepting the universe and its underlying laws{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.98,0:43:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即宇宙及其内部的定律{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}are package of marvels that just happens to be,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.28,0:43:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太不求甚解了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is deeply unsatisfying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.23,0:43:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们一定要超越自我{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I think we must go beyond,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.72,0:43:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们一定能超越自我{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and I think we can go beyond.{\r}
